I posted an issue before about TF logging the conv algorithm in use (pytorch has an option for this): https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/8941 

This probably isn't a huge issues, but one issues is that TF will have to transpose the weights on each forward / backward pass: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/8287 (and https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/7187#issuecomment-285191193).

@Yangqing also had some comments on workspace size (`TF_CUDNN_WORKSPACE_LIMIT_IN_MB`?): https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/issues/7187#issuecomment-290209116 that I don't fully understand.
